  "remarks": "LLC Gumich RTK is a Russian company producing Impulse-M robot platforms, which are intended to be used in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine and have already been tested on the field by Russian Armed Forces as of summer 2024. Therefore, LLC Gumich RTK is supporting, materially or financially, actions which threaten the territorial integrity of Ukraine.",
